        <mxCell id="XZpaEk4sSjdcldhfkn0V-37" value="Yeast sludge with flavourless meat lower moral. Sugar is one option, but reduces yeast nutrients. The lab can synthesize flavours to add to the daily meals to improve morale." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#333333;fontFamily=Times New Roman;" parent="1" vertex="1">
